[TUGAS]

Buat materi pembelajaran dalam format JSON.

[SKEMA_KELUARAN]

{
"judul_utama": "",
"konten_markdown": ""
}

{% if image_context %}
[MULTIMODAL IMAGE CONTEXT]
{{ image_context }}

*** ABSOLUTE INSTRUCTION FOR IMAGES ***
The reference text above has markers like [IMG-001] (filename) - Deskripsi: ...
If you want to include an image from the context in your generation, you MUST use markdown reference-style links.
Format: ![Alt Text Singkat][IMG-001]
Pastikan Alt Text (teks di dalam kurung siku pertama) sangat singkat (maksimal 3 kata). DO NOT write the image URL, path, or base64 data. Just use the exact image ID (e.g., IMG-001) in the reference brackets.
Place the image naturally in the paragraph or section where it is most relevant.
{% endif %}

